data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT Just in time for the Holidays!  Come check out this PERFECT family home in beautiful Waterset! This 3 BR PLUS a loft, 2.5 Bath home is a popular David Weekley home and has the quality of construction and elegant finishes to show it. BONUS - This home has an ASSUMABLE VA Mortgage (for eligible Buyers) at less than 3% interest.  The home was Built in 2018 and looks brand new.  Walk into your welcoming foyer, with a half bath discreetly tucked away behind the front door, then into your large Great Room with plenty of room for the whole family.  You'll see the open floorplan includes the Kitchen overlooking the Great Room, with a huge Island Bar, granite counters, gleaming white cabinets, and marbled backsplash, all flowing into an adjacent dining area. The Great Room and Kitchen/ Dining area overlook a HUGE backyard, that's fenced and landscaped, with plenty of room to add your own tropical pool, spa, and oasis.  Upstairs in the well-designed home, you'll find a large Bonus Room/ Loft that could easily be turned into a 4th Bedroom or an Office.  There's the Master Suite, which is a large and relaxing retreat with its ensuite bathroom that includes a very large walk-in tile shower, double vanities, and a LARGE walk-in closet with plenty of storage.  Across the hall from the Master Suite are two secondary bedrooms, both spacious and with roomy closets. There's a spacious shared bathroom between the two secondary bedrooms.  There's also a Large Laundry Room upstairs for keeping all the dirty laundry away from the entertaining areas downstairs. Altogether this home boasts just over 2,000 square feet of living space, a large 2-car garage, a beautiful corner lot and a lovely contemporary appeal with all the right touches for a growing family. Of course, the Waterset Community has so much to offer its residents with clubhouses, multiple pools, exercise facilities, tennis and pickleball courts, basketball courts, beach volleyball courts, miles of nature trails and biking paths, community activities for all ages, charter schools, and more! Come see this beautiful home today and find out why this should be your HOME SWEET HOME!!
